➜江西东乡：智慧管控施工作业
http://www.sohu.com/a/418790764_114731	30989
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200916/8d0d4e9478ee4bcf8219991c3bcf99a4.jpeg" width="550" height="344" /></p>
